        slug: 'wpc-certificate',
        title: 'WPC Certificate',
        subtitle:
            'A WPC Certificate, also known as a WPC License, is an official document from Indias Wireless Planning & Coordination (WPC) Wing. This wing is part of the Department of Telecommunications (DoT) under the Ministry of Communications.',
